<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1432746-is-anyone-else-confused-as-to-what">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Is anyone else confused as to what happened when Lucy &amp; Lily were locked in the priest hiding holes and why Lucy never told Edward about this once she remembered? They were back in the house only a few days later, I can't believe she wouldn't have wanted to open the hole and recover Lily's body! Would've saved Edward a lot of heartache thinking Lily betrayed him and just run off. I think I am missing something. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
