	<tr>
		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="What&#39;s the Name of That Book???" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/21989986-solved-adult-mystery-where-female-historian-is-drawn-in-by-a-photo-of-a">What&#39;s the Name o...:</a>
        </b>
      
			<a class="actionLink" href="/topic/show/21989986-solved-adult-mystery-where-female-historian-is-drawn-in-by-a-photo-of-a">SOLVED. Adult Mystery where female historian is drawn in by a photo of a woman and finds the house where it was taken. [s]</a>
		</td>
